	   <tr><td colspan=2>Currently I have hit a wall in exp. I just dont know where to go even though I know I should go back to Derv's (I am level 11). Unfortunatly I'm over in Qeynos switching from Prim to alternate for stuff. SHould I run and get into a bandit camp in karanas, or get port to WC?<br><br>p.s: How should I twist Brusco's, and how usful is it in soloing and groups?<br>&nbsp;<br>Forest Enforcer</td></tr>
